Calculate USHE Element d_05 (End Search Date)

Source: R/dws.R
d_05.Rd

Calculate USHE Element d_05 (End Search Date)

Usage

d_05(input_df = usheUtils::fake_dws_df, with_intermediates = FALSE)

Arguments

input_df

A Data Frame. Must contain the following data fields: (end_search_date).

with_intermediates

Boolean: Option to include intermediate calculated fields.

Value

Original data frame, with USHE data element d_05 appended. Will also return appended intermediate calculated fields, if option is set.

Details

USHE Documentation

  • ELEMENT NAME: End Search Date

  • FIELD NAME: d_end_date

  • FIELD FORMAT: Varchar, 8 Characters (YYYYMMDD)

  • DEFINITION: The calendar date of the End Search Date.

d_05()
